summary: An ordinance providing for the acquisition by condemnation of certain lands, property and property rights for a right-of-way for sewer purposes over and across a portion of Blocks 27 and 41, Homecroft Addition, Blocks 2 and 6, Winship's Addition, and across a portion of the northeast one-quarter of Section 36, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W. M., and providing for payment therefor.
